Package gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractGridBagLayoutJPanel
    Abstract class that defines a JComponent with a GridBagLayout as layout manager.
    AchievementLabel
    This class is used to display the achievements in the game.
    AchievementsScrollPane
    This class is used to display all the achievementLabels in a scrollable pane
    ArenaLabel
    This JLabel contains the arena image with the puck and players on top.
    CreditsPanel
    Panel to display the creators of the game.
    ExceptionPanel
    Class that displays the exception message in a dialog and optionally exits.
    GameOverPanel
    This panel displays the status of the game after its completion.
    GamePanel
    This panel integrates the logic to update the game state and draw each frame.
    GUI
    Main class to start the GUI process.
    IconButton
    Class that creates a button with an icon and predetermined size.
    Main  
    MenuPanel
    This panel contains the game logo and has buttons to start a new game, load a saved game, change settings, show credits and exit the game.
    PausePanel
    Class that extends JPanel and works as a pause menu.
    SettingsPanel
    This panel shows the current settings and allows the user to change them.
